README

Mepis 3.4-3 baghira style splashy theme
----------------------------------------

Splashy theme for SimplyMEPIS 3.4-3, based in Baghira kwin style
Author: Martin Gallardo
mail: miga@esfera.cl
Deviant page: http://miga.deviantart.com/

Included mepis_baghira_set.xcf file to edit in The GIMP.

Installation
-----------

extract the file tar gz file to any folder:

tar xzf mepis_baghira-VERSION-theme.tar.gz

then move the mepis_baghira folder to /etc/splashy/themes

and run: 

sudo splashy_config --set-theme mepis_baghira

Enjoy!!!
